      "fields": {
        "title": "Dune",
        "slug": "dune",
        "synopsis": "Set in the far future amidst a sprawling feudal interstellar empire where planetary fiefdoms are controlled by noble houses, Dune tells the story of young Paul Atreides as he and his family accept control of the desert planet Arrakis.",
