        "title": "Educated",
        "slug": "educated",
        "synopsis": "Tara Westover was seventeen the first time she set foot in a classroom. Born to survivalists in the mountains of Idaho, she prepared for the end of the world by stockpiling home-canned peaches. Her quest for knowledge transformed her, taking her over oceans and across continents, to Harvard and to Cambridge University.",
